 
----------------------------------------------------------
Cross Build Tools

500mc develoment environment-- install the e500mc cross build tools with ltib)

    * the bin directory to the tools must be in your path
    * like the Linux kernel you must set the CROSS_COMPILE
      environment variable with the prefix of the tools you are using
          $ export CROSS_COMPILE=powerpc-linux-gnu- 

----------------------------------------------------------
Getting, building the hypervisor

    * prerequisites are dtc (device tree compiler), libfdt, and
      libos libraries
          o recommended location to put these libraries is at the same
            level as the hypervisor source.
            i.e. your directory structure should look something like:
                hv
                dtc
                dtc/libfdt
                libos

    * dtc & libfdt
          o export http_proxy=http://wwwgate0.freescale.net:1080/
          o git-clone http://www.jdl.com/software/dtc.git dtc
          o build dtc
                $ cd dtc
                $ make 
          o libos
                $ git-clone git://auslxsc02.mtwk.freescale.net/git/libos.git libos 
    * to get the hypervisor
          $ git clone git://auslxsc02.mtwk.freescale.net/ultravisor.git hv 
    * to build the hypervisor
          o cd hv
          o make allyesconfig
          o make 
    * to build the tests
          o cd hv/test
          o make 

----------------------------------------------------------
Source tree directory structure

   The hypervisor uses libos and the libfdt library from the device
   tree compiler.  Descriptions of the source directories are 
   below:

   dtc/libfdt		The libfdt library for device tree processing
   libos/include        libos library includes
   libos/lib            libos library source
   hv/src               hypervisor source
   include              hypervisor includes
   tools                misc tools
   tools/mux_server     The UART multiplexer-- runs on a host system
   tools/partman        The Linux user space partition manager tool
   test                 Hypervisor unit tests
   test/common          files shared by the tests

